                                        <lb break="no"/>θοῦντος</q>,<milestone n="61" unit="section"/>καὶ ὡς <persName ref="#thoukydides"><name xml:id="name_ogh_m2j_jx">Θουκυδίδης</name></persName> <note resp="bethe">(IV 1, 1)</note> <q>περὶ σίτου ἐκβολήν</q>, καὶ <note resp="bethe">(IV 6, 1)</note>
