                                        <lb/><q>δεξιώσασθαι</q>· <milestone n="160" unit="section"/><persName ref="#xenophon"><name xml:id="name_ozj_rbc_kx">Ξενοφῶν</name></persName> <note resp="bethe">(Cyrop VI 3. 36)</note> δὲ εἴρηκε καὶ <q>δεξιωσά
