                                        <lb/>22 Ko</bibl>)</note> δὲ <quote>‘†δυαδελφίδην† ταὐτῷ μυχῷ’</quote>. <persName ref="#herodotos"><name xml:id="name_wbp_zyk_1cb">Ἡρόδοτος</name></persName> <note resp="bethe">(III 65)</note> δὲ καὶ
