                                        <lb break="no"/>σθίειν — ἐξέφαγεν. <milestone n="40" unit="section"/><persName ref="#metagenes"><name>Μεταγένης</name></persName> <note resp="bethe">(I p 709. 15 Ko)</note> δὲ καὶ λαθροφα
