                                        <lb break="no"/>λια, κάρυα, μυρτίδες, μέσπιλα, ἃ καὶ ὄα καλεῖται· <milestone n="80" unit="section" edRef="#lh1706"/>καὶ τοὔνομα ἔστι
                                        <lb/><milestone n="80" unit="section" edRef="#b1931" cert="unknown"/>παρὰ <persName ref="#platon_phil"><name xml:id="name_e1s_1db_sx">Πλάτωνι</name></persName> <note resp="bethe">(Conv 190 E)</note> τοῦτο, ὡς παρ᾽ <persName ref="#archilochos"><name xml:id="name_x3z_1db_sx">Ἀρχιλόχῳ</name></persName> <note resp="bethe">( 180)</note> ἐκεῖνο.
                                        <pb n="24"/>
