                                        <lb/><title>Πλούτῳ</title> <note resp="bethe">( 815?)</note>ἶπον τὴν μυάγραν καλεῖ. <milestone n="156" unit="section"/>καὶ <persName ref="#kallimachos"><name xml:id="name_o4n_sxs_ybb">Καλλίμαχος</name></persName> δὲ ἔφη <note resp="bethe">(fg 233)</note>
